      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "We are pleased to present a superlative example of automotive preservation, currently offered in impeccable showroom condition. This vehicle retains its original luster, featuring an unblemished exterior finish and an interior that remains devoid of wear. Every mechanical system has been rigorously vetted to ensure performance that aligns with its aesthetic perfection. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast to acquire a vehicle of peerless caliber and documented excellence.",
