    {
      "id": "sybil_18_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_18",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? This car is absolutely stunning and has been pampered like one of the family. It\u2019s in truly incredible shape\u2014not a scratch or a smudge in sight! It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. Come take a look, you\u2019re going to love it!",
