    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the high-revving S54 platform, featuring the iconic 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a factory-spec 8,000 RPM redline. Performance is optimized via a Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission and a variable M-differential lock, ensuring linear power delivery and exceptional lateral grip. This chassis has been meticulously preserved, with documented reinforcement of the rear subframe, a comprehensive Dr. VANOS overhaul, and rod bearing replacement using ARP hardware. The suspension geometry remains precise with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, while the exterior displays consistent factory paint depth across all panels. A mechanically transparent, collector-grade specimen for the purist.",
